Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！　このファンデ 欲しかったやつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hmm... No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:16.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こっちのリップと スプレーマニキュアもお願い！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:16.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can bring out tanks and fighter jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:21.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ　このウイッグ　かわいい！ ボス そろそろ出発の時間ですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:21.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will stop them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}エリザは何も買わなくていいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's following the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ええ　私は何も。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he continues on it, \Nhe'll pass by in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…。 あれ　かわいかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you think he'll stick to the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:15.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}似合ってた！ よかったよね。 トイレに行って来る。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:15.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, he'll notice my presence \Njust before he gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　いいよ 荷物　ちゃんと見ててね。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because APR will start adding interest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:24.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカの奴 あのままで平気かね？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:24.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But given his speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:30.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}体のほうは　私の笛で 少しは回復したと思うんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:30.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We may be able to attack him \Njust before APR adds interest. I Alone Lose When It Reaches the Heavens \NChapter 7 Bankruptcy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:34.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}暗殺の話は　お前　どう思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:34.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Knuckle's ability, Chapter 7 Bankruptcy, attaches APR to an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:37.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((「十老頭」は 「旅団」の始末をプロに依頼した))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:37.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Every ten seconds, APR informs the \Nenemy that interest will be added.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:43.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) ((クラピカ　その殺し屋のチームに 参加してもらいたい))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:43.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if the enemy is over a hundred meters \Naway from Knuckle, the interest stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:49.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}心音を聞いた限り 全てを納得した上で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:49.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When this happens, the time \Nuntil the next interest payment is remembered by APR.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:59.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}暗殺チームに 合流したわけじゃないわね。 だろうな。 でも　クラピカには 何ものよりも先立つ決意がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:59.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once the enemy is back within \NKnuckle's hundred-meter range, APR picks up where it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:05.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分の全てを犠牲にしても それを優先している 結果の判断だと思うわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:05.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's approaching at a speed between \N160 and 180 kilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:13.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダルい生き方だな。 俺にゃ　マネできん 自分を殺す人生に意味あるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:13.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If there are still three seconds or more \Nbefore APR adds interest again, there's a good chance we can \Nattack before he notices us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お嬢様　遅いですわね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人生いろいろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:33.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何に重きを置くかは 人それぞれだわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:33.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the last second, he suddenly changed direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…！ あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's down below! Knuckle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't bother. We can't catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:42.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お嬢様が　いません！ えっ？ 何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:42.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our opponent has a cheetah's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パパのウソつき！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He isn't supposed to know \Nhow to deal with Zetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うまいこと言って　本当は私を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How did he discover our ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オークションに 連れて行きたくないんだわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}入れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Look up! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:16.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひの　ふの　み　よ いつ　む…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:16.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've discovered two suspicious figures. What should I do? Ignore them. They aren't the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:19.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全員　揃ったようだな。 いや　まだだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:19.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No point in doing more work than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:26.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　チームは８人のはずだろ。 ノストラードが １人　新たに連れて来るそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:26.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, sir. It appears they were trying \Nto ambush Cheetu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:31.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ！　あのインチキ占いの オベッカ野郎か。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:31.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, he's in the area? I warned Cheetu-sama before he ran into their trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:50.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}依頼は「幻影旅団」の抹殺。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:50.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is Leol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:55.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今夜　再開される競売に 奴らが　また来るかもしれねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:55.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The target just engaged a squad of \Nsoldiers in the city of Longtong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:05:01.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}現れたら始末してくれ やり方は任せる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:05:01.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Longtong? Head north and try to cut it off. Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:04.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一応　同じ標的を狙うチームだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:04.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}連絡の際の 呼び名を決めておこうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Looks like even the army can't handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}色でいいだろう 俺はブルーと呼んでくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No... Well, they're only there to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:12.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺はレッドで…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:12.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They've had to stay in one area \Nfor a longer period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:19.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　お前らは？ シルバ。 ゼノじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:19.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After all, it's been moving constantly \Nfor over thirty hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Diego has fallen into enemy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の名を呼ぶのは自由だが 指図は受けない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you stay in your homes, you'll be killed! Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達のやり方でやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rebel scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:37.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シルバ　ゼノって… まさか　ゾルディック家か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:37.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn... Diego just appeared on TV, \Nlooking alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:46.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}同業のよしみで ３割引きで請け負うぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:46.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll have to give up my instigation. My only option is to take out as many \Npuppets and soldiers as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼らがキルアの家族…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should I go north next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:05.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　あの「旅団」だぞ 単独でやるには　ヤバ過ぎる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:05.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I knew it. Someone's still following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:13.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたは？ 拙い連携は　混乱を招くだけだ 私は一人で十分。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:13.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Who's there?! If you want something, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:22.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ…　５対４　決まりだな。 オークションの開始は９時 会場までは　我々が送る。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:22.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The presence has completely vanished. It might be following me until \Nmore Chimera Ants show up. I'm gonna shake it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それまで待っていてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It can't outlast me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:31.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よう　ノストラード 調子は　どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:31.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yo... Yo. Sorry for stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁまぁだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nah, I was headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:37.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁまぁねぇ… 偉くなったもんだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:37.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King's in this direction, right, Hagya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}つい　この間まで　片田舎の いち組長だった野郎が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, I know. It's Leol now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:44.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今じゃ　この俺と タメ口きけんだからなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:44.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then you did that on purpose? You're still a bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何でも　もみ手のし過ぎで 手を　やけどしたそうじゃねえか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Flutter's warning was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫か？　アハハ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right now, I'm trying to avoid fights... I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}男のジェラシーは見苦しいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}By the way, what's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　てめぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No idea. A Hunter hit me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ？　この野郎　あ？ 刺すなら刺してみろよ　ごらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It follows me wherever I run. Not sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ　やめろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But so far, it doesn't seem to have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:15.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言っておくがな 誰も　てめぇらなんぞ 認めてねえからよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:15.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you want me to get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の成功を妬む奴が多くて困る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm glad you're so understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　俺は　まだまだ上へ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Figured. The Royal Guard has assigned me a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネオンの予言を駆使してな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd like your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の働きには期待している。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Leol-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}十分な見返りは用意するつもりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've spotted the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's headed north on the road through \Nthe forest northeast of Longtong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}警察署長は その市長の子飼いの男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're chasing down a human. He's probably a Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}交通規制くらいは朝飯前だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And you want me to help hunt him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You said he's a Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしもし。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They can be tough to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　クラピカ　大変！ ボスが逃げちゃったの！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Of course, so I've planned ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:11.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}トイレで着替えた上で 逃げてるから 計画的みたいなのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:11.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Shaiapouf-dono has prepared \Na power tailored for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だとしたら　行き先の見当はつく。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He will teach you to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホテルに戻って待機してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}With luck, you can master it in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうした？ お嬢さんが逃走したそうです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm a slow learner, so mine took me \Nthree days to get the hang of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:25.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何!? 行く先は　我々と同じでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:25.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sounds like a sweet deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オークションか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In return, I swear loyalty to the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソ！　電源を切っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Exactly... Easy enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　ネオンは 参加証を持っていない。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sure, I just wanted an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}会場どころか検問で　はねられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're a sharp fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:44.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ライト＝ノストラードだ 検問中の全警官に指示を頼む。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:44.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you accept, return to the castle, master your new power, \Nand then contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}参加証を持たない １７１８歳くらいの娘が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In the meantime, I'll have my underlings \Ndetermine the target's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}検問所に来たら保護してくれ！ 特徴は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, I guess I owe you one. Might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＯＫです　どうぞお通りください。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, you're still all about stealing glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:04.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}検問　通れなくて困ってたの ホントに　ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:04.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was once king of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どういたしまして。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Obviously, you're looking to retake the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:13.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL] 本当か!?　それは　いつだ？ ほんの５分前です。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:13.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, I'm being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}髪形と服装は　データと 少し違いましたが　恐らく。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And he's way out of yo-yo range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　参加証は 持っていなかったんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I don't lose him or defeat him, I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「でも　私のパパは…」と 言いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's a jungle over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:32.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}結局　引き返して行きました。 はい　タクシーに１人でした。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:32.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The leaves are dense enough, he shouldn't be able to see me from the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:36.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　はい　失礼します。 ご苦労さま。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:36.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he descends to follow, \Nhe'll be in range of my yo-yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}市内の地図は　ありますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He isn't coming? Did I lose him? But in that case, he should \Ncome looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't have time to wait around! Hurry up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰だったかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can't hide from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:05.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}得意だよ 偉い人にも頼まれるし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:05.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Go forth, soldiers of Leol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どれくらい当たるの？ 百発百中なんだって。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Capture your prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:16.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「なんだって」って… 君が占ってるんでしょ？ 勝手に手が動いちゃうの。 へぇ　すごいね！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:16.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Something's coming, but from the opposite side, and it's on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:35.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どれどれ？ クロロ＝ルシルフル 変わった名前ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:35.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He removed his foe's head \Nand arms with one swing! I can't beat him in a one-on-one, \Nclose-quarters fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:42.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アハハ！　何それ　もっと変！ フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:42.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Captain! Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オークション会場の セメタリービルの中にいますね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm gonna die—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　できたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're attacking him en masse, in the treetops,\Nand we can't even touch him! Retreat! Time to regroup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見ていいかな？ もちろん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't let you escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:26.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私の占いって変わってて ４つか　５つの ４行詞からなってるのね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:26.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You must be the leader. I'll eliminate you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}へぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How'd you like that blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd guess he has a power that \Nlets him track my location. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すごいね　合ってるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't show him the cards \Nin my hand, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:26.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この１つ目の詞なんだけど…。 えっ？　あっ　ダメダメ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:26.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't want them to learn \Nof my lightning or yo-yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私ね　自分の占い　一切見ないの。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The ideal scenario would be to lose \Nthem and go back into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that's looking impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:35.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるべく 自分が　かかわらないほうが 当たる気がするから。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:35.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll have to defeat them all without using—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ １つだけ聞いてもいいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:44.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この詞には　死者の鎮魂を 想起させる部分があるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:44.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's something stuck to my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君は　死後の世界ってあると思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A flea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}占いは　あくまで 生きている人のためのもの…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A flea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この場合は　クロロさんのね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　そういう表現があったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where did it come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:11.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}慰められるのは霊じゃなく あなたのほうだと思う。 確かに　そうかもしれない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:11.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Area TH-88, X-15, Y-12, Z-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行こうか　そろそろ オークションの下見の時間だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Point X-9, Y-3, Z-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:27.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}小さい頃　テレビで見た 占い師が言ってたの。 「占いは　今を 一生懸命　生きている人を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:27.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:35.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}幸せにするためのもの」って。 そう。 だから　その占い師は なるべく悪いことばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:35.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}from my Fleadom, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「そうすれば　みんな そうならないように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}願ったり 努力したりするでしょ」って。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The bleeding won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:53.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私　その時　「ああ　そうだな」って すごく感動しちゃって。 それから ずっと占い師に憧れてたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:53.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}These fleas are more than just big bugs... Area P-9, Y-7, X-8, Z-4. Point Y-5, X-3, Z-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:45.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何年かして　その占い師の人 詐欺罪で捕まったんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:45.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And when you factor in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:57.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひょっとして「銀河の祖母」？ そうそう！ そういえば　彼女は 死後の世界　否定派だったね。 そうなの だから　私も信じてないんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:57.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}my air gun's power, they become unstoppable, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No wonder those apes couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:09.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　死んだ　そいつが 一番やりたがってたことを してやろうと思ってね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:09.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I keep running around, it'll be \Nharder for them to snipe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何それ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I have to conserve stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！　大丈夫ですか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ah, he's going to try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早く医者を呼んでくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He may try to use his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こちら　１階北側エレベーター前。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's see what he can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　急病人だ　救急車を。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:45.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　ノストラードファミリーの 娘さんだぞ！ [TV]　てめぇ 責任とれんのかって伝えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:45.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My Super Eye allows me to observe a target
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ！　聞こえたよ 「十老頭」にもファンがいるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}from multiple angles via my Satellite Dragonflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仕方ねえ　手配する！ おい　救急車を呼べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No ability you use can escape my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい！ このモニターの 画面だけを巻き戻して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, let's see what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:17.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐ろしく早い手刀… 俺でなきゃ　見逃しちゃうね 久々に血が騒ぐぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:17.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Killua cannot use En. Expanding his aura around him \Nand maintaining it for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の獲物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is by no means his forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:25.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５階の５０１号室で 休んでいるそうです。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:25.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And so, he keeps his aura within \Nthe range he can best manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:42.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}参加証を手に入れるツテなど ないはずなのに 一体　どうやって…。 お嬢さんの写真が ハンターサイトにアップされています。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:42.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In other words, the moment a projectile is \Nwithin fifty-seven centimeters of his body, Killua must rely on his incredible reflexes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:47.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何？ 恐らく　ハンターサイトで お嬢さんの写真を手に入れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:47.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}and physical strength to react \Nwith desperate speed, and dodge at point-blank range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:54.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}近づき ここへ連れて来た人物がいます。 捜し出して　ぶっ殺してやる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:54.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But this time, he didn't dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:17:00.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}落ち着いてください。 恐らく　相手の目的は お嬢さん自身ではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:17:00.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All to determine the angle of \Nthe projectile's approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}例えば　ビルへの侵入に際し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn... It came from this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:11.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここにいては危険です。 センリツ達には　連絡しました もうすぐ来るでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:11.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He let himself be hit, so he \Ncould locate the sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らに任せて大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The target is quickly heading your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:15.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボスも一緒に ついていてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:15.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:22.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありません。 ここは戦場になります。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:22.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I somewhat expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オークションは また中止になるでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The bleeding's stopped anywhere \Nthat the fleas only scratched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:35.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}血の道しるべ わざと垂らしておく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:35.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They must secrete some chemical that \Nstops blood from clotting naturally. If I start bleeding in too many \Nplaces, I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:41.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}同類にのみ分かるように 香るように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:41.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間だ　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:50.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺と同じ　殺人中毒者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:50.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can see clearly in every direction. How do you like this? There's nowhere for you to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}安心しろよ つまらないトラップは使わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長からだったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This desert is massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「セメタリービルで 暴れるから来い」言ってるね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you don't have any water, \Nyou'll die of thirst in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}考えること同じね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:27.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴミ掃除しながら ビルに向かってるね。 よし　それじゃ行くか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:27.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wanted to observe you a little longer, but I guess that won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あと　団長が珍しく 暴れ方に条件つけたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was running low on stamina, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:34.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}条件？　何て。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:34.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suppose this gives us more \Ntime to talk things over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's begin with introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「大切な暦が一部欠けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because you'll be a valuable partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:08.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}遺された月達は 盛大に弔うだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:08.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have business with the King, right? I do not! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}喪服の楽団が奏でる旋律で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:18.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}霜月は 高く穏やかに運ばれて行く。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:18.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He must have a reason for approaching me. I can't tell him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:22.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}菊が葉もろとも涸れ落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:22.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? Aren't you guys here to defeat the King? "You guys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:31.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}血塗られた 緋の目の地に臥す傍らで それでも あなたの優位は揺るがない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:31.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yep... I've been watching you since \Nthat other kid was with you. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:36.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}遺る手足が半分になろうとも。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:36.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And you felt that I would put up \Nless of a fight than Killua!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:39.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}幕間劇に興じよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:39.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:43.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}新たに 仲間を探すもいいだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:43.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You've got it all wrong! That's how you interpret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}向かうなら東がいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I guess it makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと待ち人に会えるから」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To you, I'd look like an enemy. I guess I should clear up the misunderstanding first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:57.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッハッハ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:57.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I swear that I'm not lying. I'm not looking to trick or defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:00.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハ…　おい　なぜだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:00.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハハ！　なぜだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Of course... It's hard to believe! I can sympathize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:09.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ俺は　まだ生きているんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:09.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I were in your shoes... Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:18.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この魚は 「インドアフィッシュ」といってね 閉め切った部屋でしか 生息できない念魚だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:18.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:33.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッハッハ… 死なない…　フッフッフ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:33.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is a trap. You still wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「大切な暦が一部欠けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Blood! Food! It's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:13.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}遺された月達は 盛大に弔うだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:13.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:17.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}喪服の楽団が奏でる旋律で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:17.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Captain Ikalgo's host! Crap, stop eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:22.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}霜月は 高く穏やかに運ばれて行く」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:22.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to stop, but I can't... The blood is calling to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達からのレクイエムです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't let you drag me into the water. These suction cups saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}血で血を洗う壮絶な
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, aren't you an octopus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:50.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　どこか悲しみに満ちた 嵐の夜が始まった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:50.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't call me an octopus! Killua's opponent turns out to be Ikalgo, a parasitic Chimera Ant, resembling \Nan octopus, that uses human hosts.
